View
View wraps applications and pages into a fixed, screen-fitting wrapper.
Props



Property
Value
Description




zIndex
(number)
CSS z-index property


Shortcuts




hidden

Use display: none



Defaults
{
  display: flex;
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  right: 0
}

Example
import { View } from &apos;kilvin&apos;

const App = () =&gt; (
  &lt;View style={{ backgroundColor: &apos;red&apos; }}&gt;
    I am a red page
  &lt;/View&gt;  
)
